<lyrics>[V1]
 1-fy syrka fy dẖy ạlḥyạẗ̊ swf trạk ạljmwʿ̊
 ʿsẖ ṭạhraⁿạ rwḥaⁿạ jsd̊ ḥty̱ yrwạ fyka yswʿ̊
 ạlqrạr- hl fyka yrwna yswʿ? hl fyka yrwna yswʿ?
 ạ̹lhj bh dwmaⁿạ kn ʿbdaⁿạ yṭwʿ̊ ḥty̱ yrwạ fyk yswʿ
 2- ḥyạtk ạ̉mạmhm sfruⁿ kdẖạk ạlmṭbwʿ
 hl llsmạ tqwdhm hl fyk yrwn yswʿ̊ 3-km tfrḥu ywm ạlgẖrwb̊
 ywm ạllqạ fy ạlrbwʿ
 tnẓru mn rbḥthm̊ lmạ rạ̉wạ fyk yswʿ̊ 4-fạ̉ḥyạ lh lyl nhạr̊
 kn ṣạdqaⁿạ wnfwʿ̊
 qd gẖyrka nḥw ạlmnạr̊ dʿ̊ gẖyrka yry̱ yswʿ̊</lyrics>
